OL,3,CLocals puzzled as mysterious smell
OL,4,Clike a 'damp mop' is making life
OL,5,C'miserable'
OL,7,FOn certain days it wafts across an
OL,8,Farea from Sandy Croft to Queensferry
OL,9,Fand and sometimes further, blown by
OL,10,Fthe wind.
OL,12,FIt's known as the smell ` described as
OL,13,F"smelling like a damp mop".JExactly
OL,14,Fwhere it's coming from is puzzling
OL,15,Flocals, but when it does arrive,
OL,16,Fwindows have to be closed.
OL,18,FIt's an area with industrial estates,
OL,19,Fa water treatment plant and a river,
OL,20,Fso there seems to be a range of
OL,21,Fpotential culprits.
