OL,7,F"And if you can smell, it isn't going
OL,8,Fto be one of them kind of days, you
OL,9,Fknow, where you can't open your
OL,10,Fwindows, you can't put your washing
OL,11,Fout. It's just it's just awful for
OL,12,Feverybody.J"But it comes in waves
OL,13,Fdepending on which way the wind's
OL,14,Fblowing, you know? I just sat in the
OL,15,Fbarn the other day and cried because I
OL,16,Fjust didn't want to open the front
OL,17,Fdoor, you know, knowing that's what
OL,18,FI've got to come home to."
