OL,7,FPaula, along with others who aren't
OL,8,Fhappy with the smell, have set up a
OL,9,FFacebook page to monitor when and
OL,10,Fwhere the smell is wafting.
OL,12,FA big concern is that when the warmer
OL,13,Fweather arrives and people spend more
OL,14,Ftime outdoors, things will get
OL,15,Funpleasant.
OL,17,F"Sometimes it's stronger than others.
OL,18,FBut it's just there all the time",
OL,19,Fsaid Pat Leach, who lives in Mancot.
