OL,7,FShe added: "You know, you can't open
OL,8,Fyour doors, your windows. So we're all
OL,9,Fsuffering and we don't know what long
OL,10,Fterm would be health wise, do we? We
OL,11,Fdon't know what we're breathing in."
OL,13,FResident Gareth Gealy is also fed up.
OL,15,FHe said: "You go into your bedroom and
OL,16,Fthe smell has crept into the air
OL,17,Fthrough the windows, and it's in your
OL,18,Fbedroom windows. It's in your bathroom.
