OL,3,CLocals puzzled as mysterious smell
OL,4,Clike a 'damp mop' is making life
OL,5,C'miserable'
OL,7,F"You can't sit in your garden and
OL,8,Fenjoy a cup of coffee or something in
OL,9,Fyour garden in the daytime. Or in the
OL,10,Fevenings even. So it's all invasive."
OL,12,FInevitably, the smell continues to be
OL,13,Fa major talking point.
OL,15,FFlintshire Council have carried out
OL,16,Fextensive investigations and have said
OL,17,Fthey've been doing all they can to
OL,18,Ftrack down the source of the smell.
